column2: create table ipMap ( --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- --/H describes each domain range (organization, place, hits) ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 	 ipID		    int identity(#,#) not null primary key,	--/D unique identifier 	 ipAddressString varchar(#)  not null,	--/D ip address (as a character string) 	 domainID       int  not null,	  			--/D max IP address of this domain /R ipDomain 	 webHits	    int not null,				--/D web hits from this ip address 	 sqlHits	    int not null,				--/D sql hits from this ip address 	 pageViews int not null						--/D count of page views for this ipAddress ) go
